    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. so u're saying the makeup of the population itself is the driver for the risk. to be more specific, are u suggesting that when these areas become more diverse or see higher concentrations of certain minority groups, that's what's causing the \"unpredictable social issues\" or the potential decline in the tax base u mentioned?",
